title: Install Dockfmt on Ubuntu
tags: @zettel _method docker ubuntu
roam-id: 1d55055e-c953-45d4-a7d6-e3f743331323
type: text/markdown

``` shell
sudo curl -fSL "https://github.com/jessfraz/dockfmt/releases/download/v0.3.3/dockfmt-linux-amd64" -o /usr/local/bin/dockfmt
sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/dockfmt
```
